Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 186 of the Penal Code\NA person who habitually gambles or bets shall be punished by hard labor for not more than 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SOUTH POLE ZUGAN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Souzu! Heisei Base, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(TN: Parody of the icebreaker Sōya's 1958 evacuation of Shōwa Base)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! In that case, the Souzu can't advance any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over. Wait for the weather to improve and dispatch a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all heard the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Until the helicopter arrives, we'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five of us in this first Antarctic wintering party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the helicopter only seats four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the helicopter can make two round trips in this bad weather ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subete wa God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us has to be left behind ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to beat this guy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in any case I should be able ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right? I'll say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's South Pole rules, south round only! One dealer turn for each of you and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain, so I'll be the first to get in the chopper. That's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SOUTH 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm the starting dealer.
