Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shan't cut this hatsu against toitoi ...
