Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tied for last place ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The helicopter seats six?
