Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BABA HIROKAZU AGE 24\NBORN IN IKEBUKURO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is great, as long as I don't deal in, Baba will be last!
