Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss ...
