Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Riichi tanyao pinfu ippatsu iipeikou dora dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! He gets bad draws and he deals in a lot, he's great to play against!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's play another hanchan!
