Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(TN: The Super Zugan manga is drawn by Katayama Masayuki)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that was refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go for a swim too, Toyotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather watch you swimming than swim myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I didn't know you had such talent, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning your luckletism into the manga "Ultra Zugan", and just like that, you're a millionaire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOUVEAU RICHE ZUGAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's guests to see you, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're three odd blokes who say they're boss's old friends ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We were the inspiration for Ultra Zugan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give us our royalties!"
