Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck! He's gonna turn us away at the gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fucker, enjoying all his fortune by himself! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gib it to me too! Gib me some of your fortune too, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyotomi, is it really okay to send them away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I've got a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Toyotomi! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more guests, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Just send them away!
