Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina ... it turns out I've got some business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice to meet you. My name is Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a big fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}the{\i0} Toyotomi Hideyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shook my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here, why don't I show you where I work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no desk to work on ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I do my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop raping me!
