Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have your way with me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old savings book trick always works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina, it's not what it—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Eriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were gonna to come together, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our train was a bit late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that guy's got 70 000 000 yen in savings ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's well known he's bad at mahjong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Maestro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play some mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahjong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body can't take regular mahjong anymore ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my mahjong ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who dealt in, even for just 1000 points, must take off a piece of clothing ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip mahjong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyah! Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first dealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go! Chop chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such naïve and good girls, and my haipai's good too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3p.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need chun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even need any shousangen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Hatsu only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really cut that one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Chun only! Now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no no no, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9s!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheapest out, pinfu only missing tanyao and sanshoku, now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, with that you'd skip the 9s ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron, iipeikou only! Now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron, ton only! Now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron, riichi nomi, now strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron, chun only! Ron, nan only! Ron, riichi only! Ron, pinfu only! Ron, just ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, we've been tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is actually good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I've got you cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SOUTH 1 EAST SEAT TURN 8
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this hand, you would normally cut 6m and go for 234 sanshoku using the 4m ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I don't need a high score.
