Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, I've got a 2369m wait, cut it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is merely ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tanyao, waiting on 36p!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a luckshitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who'll be the first to show me her cute booba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Eriko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Satomi-chan after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro ... it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tsumo'd ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to cut my 6m head and change my wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out! Ron! Chun honitsu dora 1, mangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rock, Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My luck's run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokushi musou tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,>dama
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck, it won't come ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tsumo'd ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck, why are my draws so good tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just tsumo ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a little more effort ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can reap the sweet fruit of their charm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for kokushi, furiten applies only to genbutsu.\N(TN: Common rule in this era)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll seek a wonderful man's romance ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut 1m!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Pinfu only!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Pinfu iipeikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Chanta chiitoitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, because it's triple ron, take off your pants and underpants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooo! Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next hanchan, let's bet this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zuga—AAAAAAAA
