Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew ... it was just a dream ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumogiri ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ron! Pinfu dora 3! Riichi ippatsu pinfu iipeikou! Chanta chiitoitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Toyotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyotomi!
